  "response": "As an AI developed by OpenAI, I don't have personal experiences or friends. However, I can share a funny story that many people might relate to:\n\n**The Great Pancake Mix-Up**\n\nA group of friends decided to have a weekend brunch together. One of them took charge of making pancakes, promising everyone a delicious stack. While preparing the batter, she accidentally grabbed salt instead of sugar. Unaware of the mix-up, she poured the batter onto the griddle.\n\nWhen the friends took their first bites, the pancakes were incredibly salty! After a moment of stunned silence, everyone burst into laughter. To salvage the situation, they got creative by topping the salty pancakes with fresh fruits, honey, and whipped cream, turning the mishap into a unique and memorable brunch experience. It became an inside joke among them, reminding everyone of the time they turned a kitchen blunder into lots of laughs.",
